# SAMPLE ENV FILE
# Cloudflare Images Configuration
# Get these from your Cloudflare dashboard:
# 1. Account ID: Go to the right sidebar of any page in Cloudflare dashboard
# 2. API Token: Go to My Profile > API Tokens > Create Token
#    - Use "Custom token" template
#    - Add "Cloudflare Images:Edit" permission
#    - Account resources: Include your specific account
# 3. Account Hash: Go to Images > Overview in your Cloudflare dashboard

CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=your_account_id_here
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=your_api_token_here
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_HASH=your_account_hash_here